          <span class="font-bold text-lg mx-12">  ★ XAI Enthusiast</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-lg mx-12 text-[#f40c3f]"> ★ Artist</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-lg mx-12">  ★ Medical AI Specialist</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-lg mx-12">  ★ Data Scientist</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-lg mx-12">  ★ Machine Learning Researcher</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-lg mx-12">  ★ Sabancı University TA</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-lg mx-12">  ★ Team Leader</span>
